trans-unit.source: Akroma is a cryptocurrency and application development platform focused on creating a governance model that will reward long-term, sustainable development and design.
Read more about our plans on Medium
The Akroma community managed mining pools.
Contact us to have your pool added to our list.
The Akroma governance model is focused on creating a sustainable application development platform while contributing back to the greater community.
Oracles are systems that provide smart contracts with data from outside the network.
Oracles are one example of the type of features that become possible with a layer of dedicated servers.
Masternodes help protect and scale the Akroma network by validating transactions and acting as a decentralization incentive. Running a masternode is rewarded with Akroma.
The masternode layer provides the foundation for additional features to be developed on the Akroma network.
Akroma offers a complete sponsorship program that can be tailored to fit your community, open source project, event or hackathons needs. Any combination of the following are available:
AKA to be used as you see fit.
Listing your community, open source project, event or hackathon on akroma.io.
Badges and flair that can be used in your promotional materials.
